{
  "text": "As an entity goes through the F process inter and finds itself in time space. It finds itself in a different set of circumstances. Could you please describe the properties or circumstances of time space? And then the process of healing of incarnating experiences that some enemies encounter. Although this query is difficult to answer adequately due to the limitations of your space, time, sound, vibration complexes, we shall respond to the best of our ability. The hallmark of time space is the inequity of between time and space in your space time, the spatial orientation of material causes a tangible framework for illusion. In time space, the inequity is upon the holders of that property known to you as time. Lacking in its tangible characteristics. Each entity is located in a somewhat immobile state, much as you are located in space time in a somewhat immobile state in time. So that it may be in the proper configuration for learn and teaching that which it has received in the space, time, incarnation, depending upon this time space locus. There will be certain helpers which assist in this healing process. The process involves seeing in full the experience, seeing it against the back drop of the mind, body, spirit, complex, total experience for giving the self for all missed steps as regards the missed guide posts during the incarnation. This is done entirely by the Higher Self until an entity has become conscious in space time of the process and means of spiritual evolution, at which time the entity will consciously take part in all decisions.",
